Package: RiboDiPA
Type: Package
Title: Ribosome differential pattern analysis
Date: 2020-01-01
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Keren Li and Jiping Wang
Maintainer: Ji-Ping Wang <jzwang@northwestern.edu>
Description: This package performs pattern similarity tests for Ribo-seq data
    with three components: P-site mapping, data binning, pattern similarity 
    test.
